data.description: Pride of Ownership 1 story 3 bedroom 2 bathroom 2 car attached garage within walking distance to Tuloso Midway Intermediate school. Home has a lovely landscaped front & backyard perfect for entertaining. Carpet free is a huge plus! Spacious kitchen with breakfast bar, dining separate, enormous living room. Owners willing to leave the main refrigerator for the new buyers to have all the kitchen appliances intact. Call your favorite Realtor to view it today!
